{"tid":137762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[終極對決有圖]一句講哂,4846生駒里奈DreamTeam定平手友梨奈Team","createTime":"2017-02-28T05:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T10:40:09.000Z","uid":16063,"like":13,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"412833da61190b9fbfe2008c422b48d3a928964a","tid":137762,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:29:00.000Z","msg":"48 46 Fes Dream Team 名單：<br />\nAKB総選挙前六－指原莉乃 渡辺麻友 松井珠理奈 山本彩 柏木由紀 宮脇咲良<br />\nAKB次總次世代－橫山由依 向井地美音<br />\n人間性器－小嶋陽菜 白間美瑠<br />\n欅坂46 W Captain－女神守屋茜 富家乖女菅井友香<br />\n乃木坂17th W C - 白石麻衣 西野七瀬<br />\n歌曲－サイレントマジョリティー<br />\nCenter－生駒里奈<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/JiXLCId.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FJiXLCId.gif&h=5502628e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/18/225636_eae67eb0801fda784b0010d0644672c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F18%2F225636_eae67eb0801fda784b0010d0644672c4.jpg&h=26db80eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坂道AKB名單：<br />\n48廁世代－岡田奈々 小嶋真子 向井地美音 小栗有以 <br />\n毫無特點三人組－長濱ねる 渡辺梨加 渡邉理佐 <br />\n無人識佢二打六－伊藤万理華 北野日奈子 寺田蘭世 今泉佑唯 <br />\n46老屎忽扮細個－救世珠理奈 發育不良齋藤飛鳥  過度發育星野みなみ <br />\nＷ櫻花－宮脇咲良 宮脇未央奈 <br />\n二世祖－菅井友香 <br />\n歌曲－47th AKB CW曲<br />\nCenter－平手友梨奈 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/6r0Xmh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F6r0Xmh.jpg&h=ddde9062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/em9YPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fem9YPE.jpg&h=3e90bce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請注意：唔係個人對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係Team對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正評：生駒里奈Team<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評：平手友梨奈Team<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"